msgid "‘idhekaccassa evarūpaṃ dukkhaṃ vedanaṃ vedayato akusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti kusalā dhammā parihāyantī’ti, evāhaṃ ajānanto ‘evarūpaṃ dukkhaṃ vedanaṃ pajahathā’ti vadeyyaṃ; "
msgstr "‘When someone feels this kind of painful feeling, unskillful qualities grow and skillful qualities decline.’ "

msgctxt "mn70:8.16"
msgid "api nu me etaṃ, bhikkhave, patirūpaṃ abhavissā”ti? "
msgstr "Not knowing this, would it be appropriate for me to say: ‘You should give up this kind of painful feeling’?” "

